{
  "texts": [
    "The capabilities that an adversary must leverage to achieve their objectives are shown in the outer layer of the objective circles.",
    "Attack classes are shown as callouts connected to the capabilities required to mount each attack.",
    "Multiple attack classes that requiring same capabilities for reaching the same objective are shown in a single callout.",
    "Related attack classes that require different capabilities for reaching the same objective are connected with dotted lines.",
    "Figure 2.2Figure 2."
  ]
}